ABOUT

   Cloud storage of useful hacks for Atlassian JIRA.


STUFF

   1. Jira userscript that does some tweaks:
      - Disable "click to edit" feature.
      - Add "Comment" button to each comment and move 
        answer form right to comment you answering to.

   2. Jira issue timeline script (in active development).
      Show various attributes of issue on time line.
      Features planned:
      - Show assignee change.
      - Show progress start/stop.
      - Show PMO request & TL response.
      - Show actually logged time (besides in-progress time).


